@@ -0,0 +1,36 @@
+Multi-tenant analytics dashboard API complete.
+
+**Features implemented:**
+
+1. **User Management** (`src/routes/users.ts`):
+   - POST `/api/users/register` - Register new users with tenant
+   - POST `/api/users/login` - Login with JWT token
+   - GET `/api/users/me` - View profile
+   - GET `/api/users/tenant` - List tenant users (admin)
+   - PATCH `/api/users/:userId/role` - Change roles (admin)
+
+2. **Data Ingestion** (`src/routes/events.ts`):
+   - POST `/api/events` - Single event ingestion
+   - POST `/api/events/batch` - Batch ingestion (up to 1000 events)
+
+3. **Query Engine** (`src/routes/analytics.ts`):
+   - GET `/api/analytics/count` - Count events with filters
+   - GET `/api/analytics/timeseries` - Time-bucketed counts
+   - GET `/api/analytics/breakdown` - Group by property
+   - GET `/api/analytics/events` - Raw event query
+
+4. **Dashboard Management** (`src/routes/dashboards.ts`):
+   - CRUD operations for dashboards
+   - Widget management (counter, timeseries, breakdown, funnel)
+
+5. **Data Export** (`src/routes/exports.ts`):
+   - `/api/exports/events.json` & `.csv`
+   - `/api/exports/dashboards.json`
+
+**Security:**
+- JWT authentication middleware
+- Tenant isolation enforced on all data routes
+- Role-based access control (admin/editor/viewer)
+- 401 for unauthenticated requests
+
+**Tests:** 19 passing tests covering all major functionality.
